after liver resection for hepatocellular carcinoma.

Gwiasda J(1), Schulte A(2), Kaltenborn A(2), Ramackers W(3), Kleine M(3), Beetz 
O(3), Klempnauer J(3), Emmanouilidis N(3), Schrem H(4).

Author information:
(1)Core Facility Quality Management & Health Technology Assessment in 
